Britannia did appear , Attended by a Sylvan Throng , And with her brought the River Nymphs along : He's dead ! he's dead ! the Genius loudly cried , On whose dear Life you did so much depend , He's dead , He's dead , she mournfully replied : Heaven would not long the mighty Blessing lend : Some envious Power , who does my Greatness fear , Foreseeing if he should to Manhood live , He'd glorious Proofs of wondrous Valour give : To distant Lands extend his Sway , And teach remotest Nations to obey : Resolved no powerful Art his Life should save , Nor I should longer my loved Gloucester have
